            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<h6>Navigation History: Let's Grow! Home &gt; Conversation Home &gt; <strong>B1 Conversation</strong></h6>\n<p><a class=\"content-link-button\" href=\"http://maken.wikiwijs.nl/94553/2_Let_s_Grow__Conversation\" role=\"button\" target=\"_blank\">Go to Conversation Home</a>  or  <a class=\"content-link-button\" href=\"http://maken.wikiwijs.nl/94574/1_Let_s_Grow__Let_s_Start_#!page-2922390\" role=\"button\" target=\"_blank\">Go straight to Let's Grow Home</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<h1>B1</h1>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">22    I can give a prepared straightforward presentation on a familiar topic within my field which is clear enough to be followed without difficulty most of the time, and in which the main points are explained with reasonable precision.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">23    I can take follow up questions, but may have to ask for repetition if the speech was rapid.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">24    I can use simple word similar in meaning to the most appropriate word to invite 'correction'.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">25    I can take a word from my mother tongue and convert it to English and ask if it's an existing English word.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">26    I can describe the features of something to make others understand what I mean.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">27    I can convey meaning by qualifying a word meaning something similar (e.g. a truck for people = bus).</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">28    I can reasonably fluently sustain a straightforward description of one of a variety of subjects within my field of interest, presenting it as a linear sequence of points. (needs rephrasing)</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">29    I can express and respond to feelings such as surprise, happiness, gratitude, sadness, interest and indifference.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">30    I can give detailed accounts of experiences, describing feelings and reactions.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">31    I can relate the plot of a book or film and describe my reactions.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">32    I can describe dreams, hopes and ambitions.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">33    I can describe events, real or imagined.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">34    I can narrate a story.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">35    I can develop an argument well enough to be followed without difficulty most of the time.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">36    I can briefly give reasons and explanations for opinions, plans and actions.</div>\n<div style=\"background:#eee; border:1px solid #ccc; padding:5px 10px;\">37    I can exploit a wide range of simple language to deal with most situations likely to arise whilst travelling.</div>\n"
                }
